            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*. The lowest-energy group of events in",
                "the He-10 spectrum was observed at approx. 3 MeV with",
                "a cross-section of approx. 140 mu-b/sr. This result",
                "is consistent with the previously reported",
                "observation of He-10 providing a new g.s. position",
                "for He-10 at about 3 MeV."
